Canada-wide warrant issued for man after shooting that killed 2 at Vaughan nightclub
By
Hannah Jackson
Global News
Posted July 29, 2022 2:34 pm
Police said a Canada-wide arrest warrant has been issued for 27-year-old Kensworth Alton Francis from Mississauga. .
York Regional Police / Handout
Leave a comment
