Donald Trump pleads not guilty to federal charges in classified docs case
Police said he has a thin build and was seen wearing a white and black shirt.Offices said he is considered “armed and dangerous.”									Story continues below advertisement
“If seen, do not approach him, instead call police immediately,” police said. “The suspect is encouraged to seek legal counsel and turn himself in.”Police also said “anyone providing assistance to the suspect may be subject to criminal charges.”Anyone with information or who may have cellphone or other surveillance footage of the incident is asked to contact police or Crime Stoppers.
