UPDATE: Canada-wide warrant issued for man sought in double homicide at Vaughan nightclub
Mississauga man wanted on 2 counts of first degree murder, 1 count of attempted murder
By Aileen Zangouei, Jeremy Grimaldi Vaughan Citizen
Jul 29, 2022
Friday, July 29, 2022
1 min to read
